title: The Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild - Delicious! Spicy! Rice goes ahead! (Doujinshi)
description:
A BotW Joke
"BotW's cooking alone is a lot of fun.
You can make so many things with all the different ingredients that even after I finished the game I went back to cook every so often."
